    <briefdescription>
<para>Software PWM on any GPIO pin. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>When hardware PWM isn&apos;t available or you&apos;ve run out of channels, this module generates PWM by toggling GPIO in a high-frequency tick ISR.</para>
